","msg":"講真 個碼頭都只係落腳地 又點會多人留係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到左埗仲唔去其他地方玩 留係碼頭托柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5966a303ddb256ce18fc72d5c9465e7411ab081","tid":189860,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:35:34.000Z","msg":"唔係講笑<br />\n<br />\n我初時真係以為啟德係禁區黎<br />\n<br />\n上年pkg，果頭係咁出貝貝，我仲同人講，啟德禁區黎，你入唔到去，死心啦"},{"pid":"7d84091cf5d213cb264eb9b0a4cbd5bfa4c06212","tid":189860,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:38:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"251cb798ba50008bf0ca1ffa35393f55411de16b","tid":189860,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人真係岸鳩，無商場就嫌無嘢行，<br />\n一邊又屌週圍商場好悶人太多，<br />\n一陣唔用個草地俾賓賓霸晒又屌</blockquote><br />\n個度真係太僻啦<br />\n除非你自己揸車<br />\n再唔係就係住附近既跑步/單車撚<br />\n唔係點會去<br />\n仲有佢開黎係俾遊客<br />\n整到交通咁不便已經係好失敗<br />\n仲有入面<br />\n係估都唔估呢個仆街碼頭用左70愈<br />\n入面連行李輸送帶都冇要用人手黎運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過最奇既係檔野咁仆街<br />\n居然來訪郵輪增長都咁快</blockquote><br />\n你見到門口條路都唔想入啦,度度都地盤起撚左十鳩幾年都未起好"},{"pid":"136dcd413d3095f99f8470fec283bd836803ce8b","tid":189860,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講真 個碼頭都只係落腳地 又點會多人留係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到左埗仲唔去其他地方玩 留係碼頭托柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係佢d接駁交通做到比屎更不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且你諗下個位置係九龍灣，本身個頭都冇野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎黎起樓好過啦，3面臨海，正過君林天下"},{"pid":"5fc7c55ff4b149ccfcb00bfffcf7e7786a3e9017","tid":189860,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講真 個碼頭都只係落腳地 又點會多人留係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到左埗仲唔去其他地方玩 留係碼頭托柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係佢d接駁交通做到比屎更不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且你諗下個位置係九龍灣，本身個頭都冇野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n接駁交通直接垃圾<br />\n有次平日入去做野，做完野走嗰陣等好耐都冇小巴<br />\n見到有架的士岩岩駛入嚟落完客就即上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ef055b142b2ea99a2fda1d0188d468e353285b","tid":189860,"uid":25971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"之前唔係話好撚大經濟效益咩"},{"pid":"455faec6dc71b736a7339441741c687143f175b8","tid":189860,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:08:51.000Z","msg":"82億war game場 正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336ee09f9d65d5319022d95dca1d92f26612e408","tid":189860,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前唔係話好撚大經濟效益咩</blockquote><br />\n97後有邊樣大基建唔係咁講"},{"pid":"8ba52fe3d68b623cb7aa0732b5b954cbd199380a","tid":189860,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日話無地  其實根本一大堆地長期浪費<br />\n<br />\n好像逸東醫院隔離  荒廢左起碼5年<br />\n<br />\n開番做臨時足球場/臨時公園</blockquote><br />\n不要再說了<br />\n英國佬係北大嶼山plan左咁多野，港共到頭來一樣都無做<br />\n有大蠔小蠔東涌西一大堆地，用一條2分鐘一班既東涌線串埋<br />\n偏偏港共好搞唔搞，係要另外搞堆死城出嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機場鐵路按計劃起四線先得"},{"pid":"91fb0127f1a427d485bdf56fbd847388a51ad1d3","tid":189860,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:19:56.000Z","msg":"星期五六日, 有人去露營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b714871a7b30a40f27a5925c088873cc1b834d3","tid":189860,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:23:42.000Z",